name: Nutrient Modifier Codes
description: NutrientModifier :  Codes for types of nutrient that is being modified such as carbohydrate or sodium.  This value set includes codes from [SNOMED CT](http://snomed.info/sct) where concept is-a 226355009 (Nutrients(substance)), and the concepts for Sodium, Potassium and Fluid. It is provided as a suggestive example.
